This is the working package to set up OSM Tile Server.
Its Installation is very easy.

Requirement: Ubuntu 10.04

1. Update and Upgrade your System

$sudo apt-get update
$sudo apt-get upgrade

2. Move to the newmap directory and run postinst script in the terminal along with installing all the dependencies

./postinst


3. This will generate a sample map at http://localhost/meramap
